column29: ["Teacher: Follow these directions to run the HubNet activity." "Optional: Zoom In (see Tools in the Menu Bar)" "Teacher: Open 'HubNet Control Center' from 'Tools' menu..." "and check 'Mirror Plots on Clients' and..." "check 'Mirror View on Clients.'" "Teacher: Press the INITIAL-LOGIN button." "Everyone: Open up a HubNet Client on your machine and..." "input the IP Address of this computer, press ENTER and..." "type your user name in the box and press ENTER." "Optional: Change any of the settings." "Teacher: Once all users are logged in..." "turn off the INITIAL-LOGIN button." "Teacher: Press the RUN-MARKET button to start." "Everyone: If you would like to sell extra oil..." "change the value of the AMOUNT-TO-CHEAT slider." "Everyone: If you would like to catch other sellers cheating..." "change the value of the ANTI-CHEAT-INVESTMENT slider." "Teacher: To rerun the activity with the same group..." "press the RE-RUN button." "[end of Quick Start instructions]"]
